</p>
<p>
Artist retains a display copy of the NFT which she may loan out at her sole and exclusive discretion.
</p>
<p>
Detail 5.	<strong>Loaning the AR Component.</strong>  Similar to the traditional rules governing a loan of conceptual artwork, the NFT may be loaned for display as long as Artist or someone from Artist’s studio is notified and oversees the installation or context of display.  The loan must be made pursuant to a written agreement clearly establishing the duration of the loan and with the clear understanding that Collector must remain the owner of the NFT for the duration of the loan.  If the NFT ownership is transferred during the course of the loan, the loan agreement will be automatically terminated, and the transferring Collector will be solely responsible for any consequences of such termination.
</p>
<p>
Detail 6.	<strong>Use of Blueprint.</strong>  This Blueprint may be copied, redistributed, remixed,  transformed, and built-upon for any purpose including commercially, with credit given to Sarah Conley Odenkirk for the original crafting of this text along with a statement detailing any changes made.
</p>
<p>
Detail 7.	<strong>Representations and Warranties.</strong>  Artist represents and warrants that she is the creator of the Artwork associated with the NFT, and to the best of her knowledge, nothing in the Video, the physical objects, or the NFT violates any intellectual property rights.
</p>
<p>
Detail 8.	<strong>Intellectual Property Ownership.</strong>  Except as set forth above regarding the Blueprint, all intellectual property pertaining to the NFT, the Video, and the accompanying physical nodes, including but not limited to copyright, applicable moral rights, and trademark, remains with the Artist. Except as allowed by this Blueprint, under no circumstances is Collector allowed to reproduce the NFT, the Video, or the physical artworks in any medium or create derivative works without Artist’s specific written consent.  Collector’s purchase of the NFT entitles the Collector to ownership of that NFT, and the rights to display the NFT as set forth in Section 4 above, and to resell the NFT pursuant to the terms of this Blueprint.
</p>
<p>
Artist specifically retains the right to create derivative works and future installations.
</p>
<p>
Detail 9.	<strong>Ownership.</strong>  There is sometimes the misperception that by owning an artwork, a Collector owns all rights including intellectual property rights like copyright.  This is not the case with physical artwork, and it is also not the case with NFTs.  Even though a Collector does not have any intellectual property rights in the artwork associated with the NFT, there are definitely responsibilities that come with ownership.  The responsibilities that come with either collecting art or participating in society require attention and maintenance.  This transaction is no different, and thus, by purchasing this NFT, Collector agrees to participate in this NFT ownership pursuant to the terms of this Blueprint.
</p>
<p>
Detail 10.	<strong>NFT Resale.</strong>  Collector is free to sell the NFT at any time as long as that sale occurs completely on-chain, on Algorand or another blockchain compatible with Algorand, and the established resale royalty is paid to Artist and Artist’s collaborators.
</p>
<p>
Detail 11.	<strong>Term and Termination of Agreement.</strong>  While nothing is truly forever, Artist will use reasonable efforts to ensure that this NFT remains functional and the digital files attached are accessible for as long as reasonably practicable, which will hopefully be close to “forever”.  In the event of technological changes, migrations to new platforms or systems, or any other technology evolution or shifts not compatible with the structure and nature of the NFT; termination or destruction of the currency or blockchain on which the NFT is minted; or the inaccessibility or destruction of the link to the attached digital files for the aforementioned or any other reasons, and the Artist cannot reasonably remedy the situation, this Agreement will automatically terminate and Artist will have no further obligations hereunder.  Artist may also terminate this Agreement at any time for her sole convenience.  Upon the termination of this Agreement for any reason, Owner may retain legal ownership of any digital or physical assets in Owner’s possession, and will continue to be bound by any moral rights that exist with regard to the NFT and any physical objects acquired as a result of this Agreement.
</p>
<p>
Detail 12.	<strong>Dispute Resolution.</strong>  In the event any disputes arise out of this Agreement, the parties agree to resolve such disputes only by mutual agreement or mediation with a mutually-agreed-upon neutral third party.  The parties waive any and all rights to bring disputes to arbitration or litigation in any form or forum.  Each party will be responsible for its own attorney fees and costs.
</p>
<p>
